    {
      "id": "688974",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "kmvver",
        "uid": "112733"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t我覺得有可能，當然，這取決於印度的人民，若之後發展量體超過中國，而那時印度人的輿論是挑戰美國，那就是下一個中國\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-09-14",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "689039",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "止痛药",
        "uid": "52311"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t印度人可不会有矛盾就把你当仇人，报复你从不讲规矩。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-09-14",
